    h2 Run the demo
    ol
        li
          span.important Set up your browser. 
          ul
            li Use Chrome version 94 or later. You can check what version of Chrome you're using by typing 
              span.code.select chrome://version 
              | in the URL bar.
            li Open 
              span.code.select chrome://flags 
              | and turn on the flag 
              span.code.select enable-experimental-web-platform-features
              |.
            li Don't use Incognito or Guest mode. The API is disabled on these profiles.
            li Ensure that the Privacy Sandbox APIs are enabled at 
              span.code.select chrome://settings/privacySandbox
              |.
            li Deactivate ad-blocking extensions on the pages where you need to test the API (or create a fresh user profile without extensions). Some ad-blocking browser extensions may block some of the API's functionality if script names contain the term "ad".
            // a(href="https://developer.chrome.com/docs/privacy-sandbox/attribution-reporting-event-guide#browser-setup" noreferrer noopener) See how
            // |.
